summary: A quick batch file to edit your character, so you can play the same file without starting over.
descriptionHtml:
A quick batch file to edit your character, so you can play the same file without starting over.

I will be adding some ESP\\\\\\\'s once my computer starts letting me save my esp\\\\\\\'s, but this is just a small thing I made for me, and I thought someone else might need it. 

Open console (~)

Type: bat newstart  (as in new start not news tart)

and close console (~)

Enjoy.

-Aaron
author: Aaron
